cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.NE 

The paper is about introducing neural architecture search (NAS) to generative adversarial networks (GANs) for image generation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.GR (Graphics), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
